History of Spinomenal

Spinomenal is a software company that has been creating slot games since launching in 2014 by Lior Shvartz and Omer Henya, and they are licensed and regulated in various jurisdictions, including Malta, Sweden, Spain, and the Isle of Man.

Spinomenal is a fast growing content provider, typically releasing 1-3 new slot games every month, highlighting their passion for game development and innovation.

The game developer's parent company is SubTech Ltd, and recently announced a partnership with global iGaming brand PokerStars, scheduled to further its growth and help them reach new gaming markets.

As a result of its ever-growing catalogue of online casino games and the fact that it spans so many genres and themes, Spinomenal has a well-earned reputation as one of Europe’s leading iGaming studios, and you can enjoy all of its latest releases on our platform today.
